morgan is a 2016 british-american science fiction horror film directed by luke scott in his directorial debut and written by seth owen .   the film features an ensemble cast , including kate mara , anya taylor-joy , toby jones , rose leslie , boyd holbrook , michelle yeoh , jennifer jason leigh , and paul giamatti .   filming began on may 26 , 2015 , in northern ireland .   the film was released on september 2 , 2016 , by 20th century fox .